This a trivial example which illustrates the use of the Rage package.
It attempts to approximate the value of PI in a probabilist way.
See the HTML documentation for more details on the algorithm. 

INSTALL:

See the file README in the demos/ directory for important informations.
Just type make and execute the PiAgent file. It need the name of a boss. 
The first time, you can use the Hierarchy.class application to built a 
simple hierarchy on a single machine. 
Enjoy.

